{"id": "art-4651", "label": "Art. 4651", "title": "Art. 4651: Stabilitatea în funcţia publică", "slug": "art-4651", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1537241140\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1241\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1537241140\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 465<sup>1</sup>:\nStabilitatea în func&#355;ia public&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2045613412\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1240\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2045613412\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În situa&#355;ia în care intervin modific&#259;ri\nlegislative cu privire la condi&#355;iile de ocupare a unei func&#355;ii\npublice prev&#259;zute la art. 465 alin. (1), acestea se consider&#259;\nîndeplinite de c&#259;tre func&#355;ionarii publici care, la data ocup&#259;rii\nfunc&#355;iei publice printr-una dintre modalit&#259;&#355;ile prev&#259;zute\nde lege, au îndeplinit condi&#355;iile de ocupare prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_439701069\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1239\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_439701069\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În toate cazurile în care intervin modific&#259;ri\nlegislative cu privire la condi&#355;iile de ocupare a unei func&#355;ii\npublice, func&#355;ionarii publici prev&#259;zu&#355;i la alin. (1) au\nobliga&#355;ia ca, în termen de maximum 36 de luni de la data intr&#259;rii în\nvigoare a noilor prevederi, s&#259; efectueze demersurile necesare pentru a\nîndeplini, pe viitor, noile condi&#355;ii de ocupare la aplicarea uneia dintre\nmodalit&#259;&#355;ile de ocupare a func&#355;iei publice prev&#259;zute la art.\n466 alin. (2) lit. b).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1373903759\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1238\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1373903759\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Prevederile alin. (1) se aplic&#259; func&#355;ionarilor\npublici &#351;i în situa&#355;iile determinate de reorganizarea\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii autorit&#259;&#355;ii sau institu&#355;iei publice,\nprev&#259;zute la art. 518 &#351;i art. 519 alin. (7)-(10).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}